---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About LokumAI - Our Story" description="Discover the story behind LokumAI, inspired by Istanbul's hospitality and Turkish Delight. Learn how we're making AI as sweet and accessible as lokum.">
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-lokum-cream via-white to-lokum-coral/10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold font-display text-lokum-charcoal mb-6">Our Story</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-lokum-gray max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          The Sweet Architecture of Dreams
        </p>
        
        <!-- Team Introduction Video -->
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <video 
            controls 
            poster="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDQ1MCIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj4KICA8cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iODAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjQ1MCIgZmlsbD0iI0ZGRkVGNyIvPgogIDx0ZXh0IHg9IjQwMCIgeT0iMjI1IiB0ZXh0LWFuY2hvcj0ibWlkZGxlIiBmaWxsPSIjNjY2IiBmb250LXNpemU9IjI0cHgiPk1lZXQgT3VyIFRlYW08L3RleHQ+Cjwvc3ZnPg=="
            class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-lokum-lg border border-lokum-coral/20"
          >
            <source src="/videos/lokumai-about.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            <div class="bg-lokum-cream rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
              <p class="text-lokum-gray">Your browser doesn't support video playback.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-lokum-gray mt-2">Meet our team building artificial delight from Istanbul!</p>
            </div>
          </video>
          <p class="text-sm text-lokum-gray mt-3 italic">üé¨ Meet the LokumAI team building artificial delight from Istanbul</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Story Content -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <!-- Main Story -->
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-16">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-lokum-coral/20 shadow-lokum mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-lokum-charcoal mb-6 flex items-center">
              <span class="text-4xl mr-3">üïå</span>
              From Istanbul's Heart
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lokum-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
              In the heart of Istanbul, where the aroma of spices dances through ancient bazaars and the call to prayer 
              echoes across the Bosphorus, developers from different corners of the world discovered something magical. 
              Like travelers drawn to the Grand Bazaar's vibrant stalls, they found themselves united by a shared vision: 
              to make artificial intelligence as delightful and accessible as the Turkish Delight that have welcomed 
              visitors for centuries.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lokum-gray leading-relaxed">
              Just as master confectioners carefully layer powdered sugar on lokum, creating perfect cubes of sweetness, 
              our founders began stacking their expertise‚Äîeach bringing their own flavor, their own color, their own story. 
              One cube represented wisdom from the East, another innovation from the West, and the third, the bridge between 
              tradition and tomorrow. Together, they formed something greater than the sum of their parts: a solved puzzle, 
              a sweet solution to complex problems.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-lokum-sage/10 to-lokum-apricot/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-lokum-sage/20 mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-lokum-charcoal mb-6 flex items-center">
              <span class="text-4xl mr-3">üç¨</span>
              The Philosophy of Delight
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lokum-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Today, when developers from around the world visit our digital bazaar, we offer them what our ancestors 
              offered weary travelers‚Äîa taste of something extraordinary. But instead of rose-flavored lokum dusted 
              with powdered sugar, we serve <strong class="text-lokum-rose">              artificial delight</strong>: open-source tools, 
              intelligent APIs, and AI solutions that dissolve complexity and leave behind only the pure sweetness of possibility.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lokum-gray leading-relaxed">
              Like the merchants of old who called out <em>"Buyurun, tadƒ±n!"</em> ("Come, taste!"), we invite every coder, 
              every dreamer, every builder to sample our artificial delight. Because just as Istanbul has always been a 
              bridge between worlds, LokumAI bridges the gap between the intimidating complexity of AI and the simple joy of creation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission Statement -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-12 border border-lokum-rose/20 shadow-lokum-lg">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold font-display text-gray-800 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-2xl text-lokum-rose font-semibold mb-4">
              Three cubes. Three colors. One sweet vision:
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 font-medium">
              Making AI a delight for all.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Logo Explanation -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-lokum-sugar to-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-lokum-caramel/20">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto">
                <img src="/images/logo-with-background.png" alt="LokumAI Logo - Three Stacked Turkish Delight Cubes" class="w-full h-full drop-shadow-lg" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-gray-800 mb-6">Our Logo: Three Cubes, Infinite Possibilities</h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
                <p class="leading-relaxed">
                  Our logo features three stacked lokum cubes, each in a different color and dusted with sugar crystals‚Äîa 
                  deliberate symbol of our identity and mission.
                </p>
                
                <p class="leading-relaxed">
                  The three cubes represent the pillars of problem-solving: <strong>diverse perspectives uniting to create 
                  complete solutions</strong>. Like a solved Rubik's cube, the stacked formation symbolizes progressive building, 
                  each layer supporting the next as we reach toward AI breakthroughs.
                </p>
                
                <p class="leading-relaxed">
                  Each cube's unique color celebrates our <strong>multicultural team</strong>‚Äîdifferent backgrounds, ages, 
                  and nationalities from across continents, all rooted in Istanbul's generous spirit. The vibrant hues reflect 
                  this diversity while the sugar crystals honor traditional Turkish delight craftsmanship.
                </p>
                
                <p class="leading-relaxed font-semibold text-lokum-rose">
                  Just as Istanbul's merchants have welcomed global visitors for centuries with sweet hospitality, our logo 
                  embodies this philosophy: offering artificial delight to developers worldwide.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-lokum-pink/5 to-lokum-pistachio/5">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold font-display text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">The principles that guide our artificial delight</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Accessibility -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 bg-lokum-pink rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-3xl">ü§ù</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Accessibility</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Making cutting-edge AI approachable and usable for developers of all skill levels, 
              from beginners to experts.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Openness -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 bg-lokum-pistachio rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-3xl">üåê</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Open Source</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Committed to open-source principles, fostering collaboration and innovation 
              across the global developer community.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Delight -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 bg-lokum-lavender rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-3xl">‚ú®</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Delight</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Transforming complex AI systems into delightful experiences that bring joy 
              to the development process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-12 border border-lokum-rose/20 shadow-lokum-lg">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-gray-800 mb-6">
            Join Our Journey
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Be part of our mission to make AI as sweet and welcoming as Turkish hospitality. 
            Contribute to our projects and help us spread artificial delight around the world.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a 
              href="/community" 
              class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-lokum-rose to-delight-500 rounded-full hover:shadow-lokum-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200"
            >
              Join Community
            </a>
            <a 
              href="/projects" 
              class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-lokum-rose border-2 border-lokum-rose rounded-full hover:bg-lokum-rose hover:text-white transition-all duration-200"
            >
              Explore Projects
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
